The paper deals with the manipulation of images and classifiers, which is a common theme in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the vulnerability of deep learning systems to adversarial attacks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The iterative procedure proposed in the paper involves updating the attack perturbation, which is a common technique in multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
